Custom Configuration Framework (custom-conf)
============================================
Package: custom-conf-apache2

This package provides standard configuration of Apache2, version 2.2 and 2.4
(automatically detected).

In particular, it addresses standard configuration of:
 - error pages (<-> 'custom-conf-apache2-templates' package)
 - syslog logging (<-> 'custom-conf-rsyslog' package)
 - LDAP authentication (<-> 'custom-conf-ldap' package)
 - SSL/TLS (<-> 'custom-certificates' package)
 - listening address/interface

Apache2 mod_macro is used to allow the user to easily include the relevant
LDAP or SSL configuration where it's needed.

